{"article_id":"C0TmRtRc6szZgnBO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The House GOP heads for its annual policy retreat Thursday in a very different place on immigration than just a year ago ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"when House Speaker John A. Boehner had hoped to use the gathering as a springboard","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to push his troops to approve a broad bill","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"legalizing illegal immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Now ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"as congressional Republicans prepare to gather for another retreat ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the conversation has completely shifted .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Boehner is leading a party","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that on Wednesday , a day ahead of the retreat , will pass a bill through the House","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"canceling President Obama ' s deportation amnesty","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and boosting pro-enforcement policies .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Senate Republicans ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"who will join the House GOP for a joint retreat this year ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"will look for ways","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to push that legislation through their chamber too .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"\" Our goal here is to fund the Department of Homeland Security .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Our second goal is to stop the president ' s executive overreach , \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Boehner said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"as he outlined the immigration fight .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"\" This is not the way","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"our government was intended to work .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"The president said 22 times","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that he didn ' t have the authority","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to do what he eventually did .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"He knows the truth here ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and so do the American people . \"","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The GOP predicted near unity in Wednesday ' s House votes ,","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"signaling just how much the politics of the issue have changed over the last 12 months .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"\" They ' ve just come off an election .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"That makes a big difference , \"","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"said Rep. Ileana Ros-Lehtinen , a Florida Republican from an immigrant-heavy district","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"who has supported Mr. Boehner ' s previous efforts","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"to pass immigration legislation ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"though she also said","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"her colleagues are reacting to a strong political message from their voters back home .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" Right after an election you are very much in touch with the people ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"and the folks from their districts are expressing their concern about what they see as immigration run amok and the border crisis ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"when the president was saying ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"' Hey , the border is secure ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"'","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"But we see border kids coming through ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and that caused a real shift in the people ' s mood , \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"The votes Wednesday will come as part of the debate","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"over funding the Department of Homeland Security through September ,","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"which is the end of the fiscal year .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"Republicans have scheduled votes on one amendment","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"to cancel Mr. Obama ' s new amnesty ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"announced in November ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"which would apply to more than 4 million illegal immigrants ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"and on another amendment","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to cancel the president ' s previous 2012 amnesty","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that applied to so-called Dreamers , or young adult illegal immigrants .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Democrats called those proposals poison pills","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"and pointed to Mr. Obama ' s promise","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"to veto any legislation","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"that tries to stop his amnesties .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"They said","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Republicans were holding homeland security money hostage to their own immigration demands .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" This is frivolous , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"said House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi , California Democrat .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" Why don ' t we live up to our responsibilities in a bipartisan way here","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"to protect and defend the American people ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to live up to the character of our country ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"which is a nation of immigrants ? \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"The White House has defended Mr. Obama ' s actions as lawful and constitutional ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that previous presidents have also granted \" deferred action \" - a suspension of deportations , along with work permits","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"to allow illegal immigrants to compete legally for jobs .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"In addition to Congress , Mr. Obama ' s policy is also being challenged in the courts ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"where 25 GOP-leaning states have sued","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to stop him","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"- a unity","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that couldn ' t have been found among Republicans until recently .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Lawmakers and analysts said","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"the 2014 House GOP retreat ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"held in Cambridge , Maryland ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"was decisive in the shift .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Mr. Boehner and his top lieutenants went into the closed-door retreat","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"promising a set of principles for reform ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"they said","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"would guide the House ' s action","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"as it tried to match the Senate ' s broad legalization bill ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"passed to tremendous fanfare a year earlier .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Sen. Jeff Sessions , Alabama Republican , had armed House Republicans with a report on the costs of legalization ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and the Eagle Forum produced a report","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"arguing","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"that the GOP had little chance","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"of gaining politically from legalization .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"Meanwhile Rep. Steve King , Iowa Republican , had organized several dozen Republicans to stand up at the meeting","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"and speak out against legalization ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"arguing","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Mr. Obama couldn ' t be trusted to carry out any laws","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"the GOP passed","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"given his past behavior .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"GOP pollsters","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"who addressed the meeting","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"also told lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"that voters weren ' t fired up over the issue ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"countering what many Republicans had feared","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"after seeing Hispanic turnout hurt them in the 2012 elections .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"\" There was an accumulation of knowledge , \"","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Mr. King said in an interview Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Within a week Mr. Boehner and his fellow GOP leaders had changed their tone ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"while they wanted to move forward ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"they didn ' t have a president","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"they could work with .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"The GOP leaders suffered one more embarrassment last summer , on a bill","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"designed to combat the surge of tens of thousands of illegal immigrant families and unaccompanied children","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who stormed the border","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"trying to gain entry .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"A conservative rebellion forced the Republican leaders to pull their plans ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"which they ' d hoped to pass with the help of Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and instead negotiate with the conservatives ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"approving a bill","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that gave Mr. Obama less than a quarter of the money","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"he wanted .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"At the urging of conservatives , the House also approved a bill","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"that would have limited Mr. Obama ' s amnesty for Dreamers .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"This week ' s votes will go further ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"canceling the amnesty program altogether .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Immigrant rights advocates ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"who had long counted on at least some Republican support for legalization ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"the GOP ' s new unity was lamentable .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"\" There ' s no daylight anymore between House Republicans on immigration reform , \"","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"said Frank Sharry , executive director of America ' s Voice , an advocacy group .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"\" So much for a ' Republican divide ' on immigration , so much for the Republican attempt","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"to expand its base ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"and so much for responsible governance . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":175,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":158,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":143,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":139,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":136,"right":138,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":0,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":1,"right":134,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":4,"right":137,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":7,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":8,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":146,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":149,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":150,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":21,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nucleari